            <span>Real Estate Agents & Realtors</span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] tracking-tight text-white">
            <span class="block">Your Website</span>
            <span class="block text-emerald-300 mt-3">Sells Before You Do</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
            {description}
          </p>

          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-white font-medium mb-2">The home buyer search story:</p>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">Home buyer searching Zillow: finds 12 homes. Checks agent websites. 11 look outdated, template-y, or amateur. 1 modern site with stunning property gallery, virtual tour, easy scheduling. Guess which agent gets the showing request? In real estate, your website is your first open house. Professional gallery = buyer interest = showing requests = closings. Your site justifies your 3% commission.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTING METHODOLOGY DISCLOSURE -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-emerald-300 p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">How I Tested These Builders for Real Estate Agents</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">42 hours of hands-on agent website research</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">01</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Built real agent sites with property showcases</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Created full websites for luxury agent, residential realtor, property manager. Added property galleries, virtual tours, MLS iframe embeds. Tested how image-heavy content loads. Didn't just test features‚Äîbuilt working listing showcases.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">02</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Measured mobile lead capture from property searches</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">73% of home searches happen on phones. Tested each platform's mobile gallery load speed, form submission ease, virtual tour performance. Slow mobile = lost showing requests. Fast mobile = scheduled showings. Measured actual lead capture, not theoretical features.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">03</span>
            <div>
