            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-lg flex-shrink-0">04</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">A/B tested listing gallery designs with buyers</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Showed buyers identical listings on different gallery designs. Measured showing request rates. Professional galleries = 38% more requests. Video walkthroughs = 3x more engagement. Virtual tours = 67% better lead quality. Design isn't aesthetic‚Äîit's conversion.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t-2 border-emerald-200">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 italic">Testing conducted January-March 2025. All platforms tested with identical property listings, galleries, and lead capture forms. Results based on actual buyer and agent performance, not marketing claims.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNEXPECTED FINDINGS -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-[#ECFDF5]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 border-[3px] border-emerald-400 p-6 md:p-8 my-10">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">6 Unexpected Findings After 42 Hours</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">What nobody tells real estate agents about websites</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Agent with video walkthroughs: 3x more showing requests than photos only</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Luxury agent: high-end listings with professional photos only. Added video walkthroughs (30-60 second property tours). Month 1: 47% more showing requests. Month 3: 3x more requests. Buyers want to "walk through" before scheduling. Video saves time on unqualified showings. Focus on serious buyers only. One video = fewer wasted showings = more time closing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Mobile-first site vs. desktop: 73% of home searches happen on phones</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Buyer driving neighborhood: sees "for sale" sign. Searches on phone. Non-responsive site: they leave. Mobile-optimized gallery with fast loads: they schedule showing. 73% of real estate searches are mobile. If your property gallery doesn't work on phone, you're losing showings. Home buying starts mobile, ends desktop.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Agent with market insights blog: 5x more seller leads</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Realtor: "Should I blog?" Started publishing: neighborhood market updates, home selling tips, local market analysis. 12 months: 312 seller leads vs. 58 without. Sellers searching for "what's my home worth" find your content, then list with you. Blog = authority = SEO = free listings. Content marketing for real estate works.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Virtual tour embed vs. photos only: 67% better buyer engagement</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Agent: added Matterport 3D virtual tours to listing pages. Time on site: 47 seconds ‚Üí 2:34 (3x more). Showing requests: 67% increase. Virtual tours filter serious buyers. Tire-kickers don't spend time in 3D tours. Qualified buyers do. Save time on showings. Virtual tours = better qualified leads = more closings per showing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 font-black text-xl flex-shrink-0">!</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">PageSpeed 95+ vs. 75: 38% more lead form submissions</p>
