            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900">Luxury agent with custom site: 2x more $1M+ listings than template agent</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-1">Two luxury agents in same market. Template agent: 3 luxury listings in 12 months. Framer custom site agent: 6 luxury listings in 12 months. 2x difference. Why? Luxury sellers expect premium presentation. Template site says "average agent." Custom site says "luxury specialist." One extra luxury closing ($1.5M) at 3% = $45K commission. Custom site pays for itself 3x over in first year.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

